- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses algorithms for verification and synthesis problems, which are relevant to AI. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses algorithmic techniques for solving relevant problems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper discusses synthesis problems, which are relevant to programming languages.
